dc_title_s: Map of the surveyed part of the territory of Michigan by O. Risdon.
dc_description_s: Longitude west from Washington. Townships and range lines for surveyed areas indicated. "Engraved by Rawdon, Clark & Co., Albany." "Copy Right Secured." 1 map: col., mounted on paper; 103 x 66 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
